{"tid":1205400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少年人哪，永不要放棄！永不要放棄！永不！永不！永不！永遠都不要放棄！","createTime":"2019-06-11T18:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:35:56.000Z","uid":44698,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"681874b590b415b4f4152e0e2667f559af2990c6","tid":1205400,"uid":44698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"Young gentlemen, Never give up! Never give up! Never! Never! Never! Never!<br />\n<br />\n二戰時關乎大英祖國生死存亡<br />\n好在有首相邱吉爾帶領英國渡過難關<br />\n成功抵禦德軍入侵<br />\n<br />\n今日到香港生死存亡之秋<br />\n雖然冇人帶頭<br />\n但係我地香港人點都要撐住唔好放棄<br />\n拜託大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}